```

Key features of this solution:
1. Responsive design that works in iframes
2. Playlist support with click-to-play functionality
3. Auto-play next track
4. Visual indication of currently playing track
5. Clean, minimal styling

To get your Mega.nz links working:
1. Upload your audio files to Mega.nz
2. Get the direct download links for each file
3. Replace "YOUR_MEGA_LINK_1" etc. in the playlist array with your actual Mega.nz links

For the Mega.nz links to work properly, make sure they are public links and have the correct content disposition headers for audio streaming.

