Key things to note:
- This implementation loads 12 products at a time
- The scroll trigger activates when user reaches near bottom of page
- Products are loaded via AJAX to maintain smooth performance
- The loading indicator provides user feedback

You can adjust the number of products loaded by changing the paginate value in step 1, and customize the styling to match your theme's design.

Here's how to make your Shopify infinite scroll work perfectly on mobile devices:

1. Update the JavaScript to handle mobile touch events:

```javascript:assets/infinite-scroll.js
$(document).ready(function() {
  let currentPage = 1;
  let loading = false;
  let touchStartY = 0;

  // Handle both scroll and touch events
  function loadMore() {
    if(!loading) {
      let scrollPosition = $(window).scrollTop() + $(window).height();
      let threshold = $(document).height() - 300; // Increased threshold for mobile

      if(scrollPosition >= threshold) {
        loading = true;
        $('#loading-spinner').show();

        currentPage++;
        $.ajax({
          url: window.location.href,
          type: 'GET',
          data: { page: currentPage },
          success: function(data) {
            let $newProducts = $(data).find('#product-grid [data-product-card]');
            if($newProducts.length > 0) {
              $('#product-grid').append($newProducts);
              loading = false;
            }
            $('#loading-spinner').hide();
          }
        });
      }
    }
  }

  // Mobile touch events
  $(document).on('touchstart', function(e) {
    touchStartY = e.originalEvent.touches[0].pageY;
  });

  $(document).on('touchmove', function(e) {
    let touchEndY = e.originalEvent.touches[0].pageY;
    if(touchStartY > touchEndY) {
      loadMore();
    }
  });

  // Regular scroll event
  $(window).scroll(loadMore);
});
```

2. Add mobile-specific CSS:

```css:assets/custom.css
#product-grid {
  -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; /* Smooth scrolling on iOS */
}

#loading-spinner {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 15px 0;
}

/* Mobile-optimized loading indicator */
.loading-text {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #666;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* Mobile-specific media query */
@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
  #product-grid {
    margin: 0 10px;
  }

  .loading-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
  }
}
```

3. Add viewport meta tag if not already present:

```liquid:layout/theme.liquid
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
```

4. Optimize performance with mobile-specific settings:

```javascript:assets/infinite-scroll.js
