  productsPerLoad: 6,  // Load fewer products per request on mobile
  scrollThreshold: 200,  // Trigger loading earlier on mobile
  debounceDelay: 100   // Prevent multiple rapid requests
};
```

These updates will make your infinite scroll:
- Work smoothly on all mobile devices
- Handle touch gestures naturally
- Load efficiently to save mobile data
- Look great on all screen sizes
- Provide clear visual feedback
- Maintain good performance

The code is optimized for both iOS and Android devices and includes smooth scrolling behavior that mobile users expect.
